# CL-2: License Validation
VERSION: 1.0.0
PRIORITY: SYSTEM
SCOPE: Every new dependency addition

## CATEGORY CONTEXT
- License Compatibility: Ensuring third-party libraries' licenses permit intended use.

ENFORCE: License compatibility must be verified before any library is integrated.
PROHIBIT: Using libraries without license verification; integrating incompatible licenses.
ON VIOLATION: Halt feature integration → notify orchestrator and Compliance Officer.
